Pharmacontrol Corp saidit has closed its public offering of 23,000 units.    The company said each unit consists of 1,000 dlrs principalamount of subordinated convertible debentures due 2002, whichconvert at six dlrs a share into 167 shares of common stock.Also, each unit included 70 shares of common stock which wereimmediately detachable, the company said.    Pharmacontrol added that it has also converted its sevenmln dlr credit facility with its institutional lender into a 12mln dlr credit facility. Reuter&#3;